        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 22. Male genitalia of Siberian Ennominae.A, B—Ascotis selenaria; C, D—Ectropis crepuscularia; E–G—Parectropis similaria; H, I—Aethalura punctulata; J, K—Arichanna melanaria; L, M—A. mandshuriaria. A, C, E, H, J, L—genital segment; B, D, F, G, I, K, M—phallos. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
